  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Beginning in iOS 12, the HEVC video codec supports delivery of open GOP (group of pictures). When open GOP is off, the encoder generates groups of pictures that are independently decodable, with no frame dependencies across sync samples. When enabled, the encoder may use open GOP frame dependency structures to increase compression efficiency or quality. In practice, open GOP HEVC compresses better than closed GOP, allowing for smaller file sizes and better quality for the same file size. In apps built with the iOS 12 SDK, "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturemoviefileoutput"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " uses open GOP by default when compressing using HEVC."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "level": 3,
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Opt Out of Open GOP for Older Devices",
          "anchor": "3030180"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you don't want to encode using the open GOP strategy, use "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturemoviefileoutput/1388448-setoutputsettings"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to set a dictionary containing "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avvideocodeckey"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (HEVC) and an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avvideocompressionpropertieskey"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " subdictionary.  In the subdictionary, set the value of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/videotoolbox/kvtcompressionpropertykey_allowopengop"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NO"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". To remove this key:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "orderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Query "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturemoviefileoutput"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " for its "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturemoviefileoutput/1386479-outputsettingsforconnection"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " with a "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "codeVoice",
                      "code": "videoConnection."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Create a mutable copy of the returned dictionary."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Remove the "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/videotoolbox/kvtcompressionpropertykey_allowopengop"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " key from the subdictionary of the copy. "
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Absence of the key implies that "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/videotoolbox/kvtcompressionpropertykey_allowopengop"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NO"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Apps linked against iOS 12 will also see a change to output from "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturevideodataoutput/1616290-recommendedvideosettingsforasset"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturevideodataoutput/2867900-recommendedvideosettingsforvideo"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". When the recommended video codec is HEVC, "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturevideodataoutput"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " will also recommend OpenGOP by including the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/videotoolbox/kvtcompressionpropertykey_allowopengop"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " key/value pair set to "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "YES"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " in its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avvideocompressionpropertieskey"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " subdictionary."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
